org.jetel.component.tree.reader

Class XPathPushParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.component.tree.reader.XPathPushParser

  • public class XPathPushParser
extends java.lang.Object
    This unit traverses tree structure using given mapping. Results of the traversal are pushed into DataRecordReceiver.
